    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Reliable & Ready \u2013 A Great Everyday Car at a Fair Price! \ud83d\ude97\n\nLooking for a dependable vehicle that won't let you down? This one checks the boxes! This car is in good condition \u2014 it's been well cared for and shows normal wear consistent with regular use. You'll find it drives smoothly and comfortably, with no major issues to worry about. It's not showroom-perfect, but it's clean, solid, and ready to serve you well for years to come. If you want a trustworthy ride without paying mint-condition prices, this is a smart choice. Come take it for a spin \u2014 we think you'll be impressed!",
      "price": 33000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "A wallet-friendly opportunity for the handy buyer or someone just needing basic point-A-to-point-B transportation! We'll be straight with you \u2014 this vehicle is in poor condition and shows considerable wear inside and out, with visible cosmetic damage and mechanical issues that will need attention. That said, it's priced to reflect exactly what it is, making it a realistic option for a DIY enthusiast or a buyer on a tight budget. Come take a look and see if it's the right fit for your needs!",
      "price": 6000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in poor condition, and we want to be fully transparent with prospective buyers about what that means. The exterior shows significant wear throughout, including multiple dents, deep scratches, and areas of rust that have compromised the paint in several locations. The body panels show visible damage consistent with years of use and minor incidents. The interior is similarly worn, with torn upholstery, cracked dashboard trim, and staining throughout the cabin. Mechanically, the vehicle runs but has known issues that will require attention \u2014 expect to invest in repairs before relying on this car for regular use. This listing is best suited for buyers who are comfortable with a project vehicle, have mechanical skills or access to affordable repair services, or are looking for parts. We are pricing this car accordingly and encourage serious buyers to inspect it in person before purchasing.",
      "price": 6500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in fair condition, and we want to be fully transparent about what you're getting. The exterior shows visible wear, including multiple scratches, a few minor dents, and some paint fading in certain areas \u2014 nothing that would compromise the structure, but noticeable upon close inspection. The interior is functional with moderate wear on the seats, dashboard, and carpeting; some scuffs and minor staining are present. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it has some age-related wear \u2014 you may notice slightly rough idling or minor hesitation, and we recommend a pre-purchase inspection by a trusted mechanic. The tires have adequate tread remaining, and the brakes are serviceable. All major systems \u2014 engine, transmission, heating, and cooling \u2014 are operational, though not in like-new condition. This is a solid vehicle for a buyer willing to accept cosmetic imperfections and potentially invest in minor maintenance down the road. Priced fairly to reflect its current state.",
      "price": 16500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly as a mint-condition car and represents a truly exceptional find in the used-car market. The exterior is flawless \u2014 no dents, no scratches, no paint fading or blemishes of any kind. The paint retains a deep, showroom-quality shine, and all body panels are perfectly aligned. The interior is equally impressive: seats, dashboard, carpeting, and all trim pieces look and feel as though they have never been used. Every control, button, and feature functions exactly as intended with no issues whatsoever. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and cleanly, with no leaks, unusual noises, or warning lights. All mechanical systems \u2014 brakes, suspension, transmission, and drivetrain \u2014 are in perfect working order. Service records are available and reflect meticulous, consistent maintenance throughout the vehicle's life. This is a rare opportunity to purchase a used vehicle that truly feels new. Ideal for a buyer who demands the very best and refuses to compromise on quality.",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
